{
  "stem": "20088.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're on the way back to Holland where we hope we will find [INAUDIBLE] and Heinz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and then we went to somewhere, to Naples where we dropped off some of the Italian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we went to Marseilles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was the most fantastic welcome there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a band of music and flags and, well, a military band that was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody-- when everybody walked down the gangplank, they were clapping and playing some more drums.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and it was really, you know, we were quite taken with all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was a big-- lots of tents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything was, again, registered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got, again, different clothes and-- and food and wine and really the French way, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- then my mother volunteered again to be a translator.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, again, I was cross, because we were taken somewhere to a big hall where we had this lovely banquet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother missed that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very cross with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, always you have to go off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now you missed all this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And anyway, [LAUGHS] but she always-- she was a great busybody at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when, as a married woman, she was very subdued.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was very strong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was always in the background.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But after what, she became very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I the camp must have taught her that you have to push yourself, your way through things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, so and then I think by the evening they said, everybody who is the French, who had to go that way, stayed, of course.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we boarded a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we're going on to Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
